nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 167 is the 145th issue of Star Wars Insider magazine and the seventy-fifth published by Titan Magazines. It was released on July 26, 2016.

Insider presents our dazzling new look issue! With all-new features, amazing interviews, and a few new surprises, this unmissable issue features: New Star Wars heroes Finn and Rey profiled! Star Wars: The Force Awakens' Doug Chiang on creating designs for the Star Wars galaxy! Set Decorator Roger Christian reveals secrets of the saga as he offers a tour of the Millennium Falcon! And don't miss our amazing all-new fiction!
